creamertweet.com
--------------------

This site aim to make it possible to script/schedule twitter activity.

Once you have logged in you can set up scripts in which you schedule tweets to be posted at a given time.

A cron task runs periodically and sends out the sceduled tweets.

The site is based on the Tornado web server and framework: http://www.tornadoweb.org/
The site is backed by the CouchDB document-oriented database: http://couchdb.apache.org/

The site is running at: http://creamertweet.com/

